Fantastic teacher, probably one of the better profs at UTM. Makes the class interesting. As long as you pay attention to the lectures, you will do great in the class.

She is young enough to use videos and examples that are relevant to us students. She is so enthusiastic about sociology and it really inspires you to do the same. She is always organized, a great speaker, and really encouraging. One of my favourite profs to date! Worth taking her class.
Prof is young and new to UTSC, one of best lecturers I've ever had! Exams are on textbook, lectures, class discussion, videos. Definitely take this course with her you won't regret it
